{
    "info": {
        "name": "FHIR-MERN API - Corrected v2",
        "description": "Exhaustive API documentation for FHIR-MERN.\n\n### Environment Variables\n- `host`: e.g. `localhost:3000`\n- `protocol`: e.g. `http` or `https`\n- `origin`: e.g. `http://localhost:5173` (Required for Better Auth routes)",
